        {
          "md": "PORKY PIG in \"Porky of the Mounties\" - 24 - art only - Petunia goes to Canada for the summer, and when she fails to write him for a week, Porky decides to go to a masquerade party, as a Mounted Policeman. The wind blows Porky's hat into a boxcar, and he and Bugs are trapped inside and carried to Canada, where Porky is mistaken by Petunia's uncle for Dauntless of the Mounties. *(Mar. 21, 1944)*",
          "value": "PORKY PIG in \"Porky of the Mounties\" - 24 - art only - Petunia goes to Canada for the summer, and when she fails to write him for a week, Porky decides to go to a masquerade party, as a Mounted Policeman. The wind blows Porky's hat into a boxcar, and he and Bugs are trapped inside and carried to Canada, where Porky is mistaken by Petunia's uncle for Dauntless of the Mounties. (Mar. 21, 1944)",
          "bbox": [
